1
00:01:32,080 --> 00:01:34,990
[How dare you!?]

2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:37,970
[Episode 14]

3
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:56,220
[A few hours ago]

4
00:01:53,710 --> 00:01:54,970
You have good taste.

5
00:01:57,229 --> 00:01:58,000
Excuse me, please.

6
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,229
Have a look!

7
00:02:54,840 --> 00:02:56,240
Running into the two of us

8
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:57,960
means you're out of luck.

9
00:03:02,990 --> 00:03:03,650
Master Bei,

10
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:05,150
this mechanism of yours

11
00:03:05,150 --> 00:03:06,810
is really cleverly designed.

12
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,130
Stab me with it again

13
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:12,360
and I'll make it malfunction.
Do you believe me?

14
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:13,770
I-I believe you.

15
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:14,640
I believe you.

16
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:21,570
Mr. Bei,

17
00:03:22,310 --> 00:03:24,680
I think you should keep dressing
as a woman.

18
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,000
Your own face...

19
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,200
What about it?

20
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:28,960
It's ugly.

21
00:03:33,050 --> 00:03:35,240
So I get beaten for telling the truth?

22
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,150
Useless!

23
00:03:46,660 --> 00:03:55,070
[Shou'an Palace]

24
00:03:48,430 --> 00:03:49,870
All of you are useless!

25
00:03:56,030 --> 00:03:58,400
The Empress Dowager summoned
many strategists overnight.

26
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,560
Judging by this scene,

27
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,690
she must be furious.

28
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,360
We fought well in this battle.

29
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,520
Using Prince Duan's hand,

30
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:08,030
we eliminated the experts
around the Empress Dowager

31
00:04:08,030 --> 00:04:10,840
and dispelled Prince Duan's suspicions
about Mr. Bei.

32
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,240
Two birds with one stone.

33
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,700
Not bad indeed,

34
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,290
but let's not get cocky.

35
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:19,230
When the fight between them
is nearing its end,

36
00:04:19,240 --> 00:04:21,070
there won't be much time for you
to lie low

37
00:04:21,070 --> 00:04:22,280
and bide your time.

38
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,210
What is this?

39
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:30,750
Bai gave it to you.

40
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:34,060
Let me explain.

41
00:04:34,190 --> 00:04:35,250
No need to explain.

42
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,000
It's rare for him to be so thoughtful.

43
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:37,730
Just keep it.

44
00:04:40,870 --> 00:04:41,470
That's...

45
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:42,950
That's it?

46
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,270
What else should I do?

47
00:04:46,950 --> 00:04:48,880
Stop pretending to be so generous.

48
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,600
Aren't you usually quite jealous?

49
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:51,830
So what if you're the emperor?

50
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,270
Can you guarantee she won't be bullied?

51
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,000
That I can do.

52
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,750
Then can you guarantee

53
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,360
that among all the women in the world,
she'll be the only one you want?

54
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,090
That's easy.

55
00:05:02,390 --> 00:05:03,000
You...

56
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:06,210
don't have anything else
you want to say to me?

57
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,180
What else should I say?

58
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:09,900
You tell me.

59
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,290
The Empress Dowager

60
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,750
will definitely find every excuse

61
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,450
to make things difficult for Prince Duan.

62
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:23,800
So let's...

63
00:05:24,270 --> 00:05:25,070
Let's do what?

64
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:28,510
Let's...

65
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:35,720
No rush.

66
00:05:37,580 --> 00:05:39,840
Let's wait until everything's settled.

67
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,930
I really can't understand.

68
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:47,040
Why did Concubine Yu do such a thing?

69
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:49,120
She's already
the most favored in the harem.

70
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:51,320
Why did she do something so despicable?

71
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,350
That servant

72
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:54,370
kept insisting it was his own idea

73
00:05:54,430 --> 00:05:56,230
and had nothing to do with her.

74
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:59,040
Concubine Yu really managed
to wash her hands of it completely.

75
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,170
Wash her hands of it?

76
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,650
Then why did she end up
in the Cold Palace?

77
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,540
Let me tell you,

78
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,560
she's miserable in the Cold Palace.

79
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,390
Nonsense.

80
00:06:06,390 --> 00:06:07,560
Who's talking nonsense?

81
00:06:07,560 --> 00:06:09,160
Go to the Cold Palace
and see for yourself.

82
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:10,000
How dare you!

83
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,470
Why are you cursing at me?

84
00:06:12,070 --> 00:06:12,470
Mr. Li.

85
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:14,680
Mr. Li.

86
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,730
Noble Consort Yu

87
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:18,430
understands the greater good and
loves the people like her own children.

88
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:20,680
How could she do something so despicable?

89
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,340
Don't spread rumors anymore.

90
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:23,480
Yes.

91
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,810
There must be some misunderstanding.

92
00:06:31,940 --> 00:06:34,400
I must go ask His Majesty
for clarification.

93
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:37,870
But harem affairs
are His Majesty's family matters.

94
00:06:37,870 --> 00:06:39,930
How can I, a mere subject, interfere?

95
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:41,950
The Noble Consort once saved my life.

96
00:06:41,950 --> 00:06:43,360
Now that she's in trouble,

97
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:44,720
how can I just stand by?

98
00:06:52,290 --> 00:06:53,620
But as a court official,

99
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,810
what can I really do for Her Highness?

100
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,800
Li Yunxi, oh Li Yunxi.

101
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:02,160
So you're such a coward.

102
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,800
She is not only His Majesty's consort

103
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,800
but also his comrade
who fights alongside him.

104
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,950
Are you going to be like those pedantic,

105
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,390
narrow-minded fools

106
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,120
and abandon her after using her

107
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,890
just because she is a woman?

108
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:18,070
Your Majesty!

109
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,190
I

110
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:24,340
am willing to counsel
even at the cost of my life!

111
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:29,290
You're here?

112
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:32,250
Come.

113
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,930
Please rise.

114
00:07:35,830 --> 00:07:36,630
Don't mind me.

115
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,510
You two talk.

116
00:08:07,430 --> 00:08:08,270
Since everyone is here,

117
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:08,800
let's...

118
00:08:09,160 --> 00:08:09,630
begin.

119
00:08:28,830 --> 00:08:30,920
The one who killed someone last night
was Li Si.

120
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,470
You're not a wanted criminal.

121
00:08:32,470 --> 00:08:34,000
Why are you being so sneaky?

122
00:08:34,510 --> 00:08:35,309
That's right.

123
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:38,720
I've been

124
00:08:38,909 --> 00:08:40,440
hiding so carefully all this way.

125
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,169
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

126
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,870
Why did you use internal force
just to throw a bag?

127
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,400
Alright.

128
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,040
Stop fooling around.

129
00:08:51,690 --> 00:08:53,090
To avoid complications,

130
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:55,840
I have to hastily arrange for you
to leave the city.

131
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:56,770
Have you decided

132
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:57,500
where to go?

133
00:08:57,790 --> 00:08:59,840
I'll stay at a farmhouse for a few days

134
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:01,270
and wait for my companion
before we leave together.

135
00:09:01,270 --> 00:09:02,000
Companion?

136
00:09:04,870 --> 00:09:05,960
You rascal.

137
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:08,120
You're quite something.

138
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:10,310
It's only been a few days,

139
00:09:10,550 --> 00:09:13,610
and you've already gained
His Majesty's recognition.

140
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:15,670
What's his secret order

141
00:09:15,670 --> 00:09:17,200
that you can't even tell me?

142
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:20,120
You'll have to ask His Majesty.

143
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:22,990
Forget it.

144
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:25,240
Now that Dan

145
00:09:25,870 --> 00:09:27,400
is in a dangerous situation

146
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,300
and you're still inexperienced,

147
00:09:29,670 --> 00:09:30,240
you must

148
00:09:30,510 --> 00:09:32,240
be extra careful in everything

149
00:09:32,910 --> 00:09:34,670
and act only after careful planning.

150
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:36,390
Don't let him down.

151
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,600
Also,

152
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,800
take good care of yourself.

153
00:09:40,800 --> 00:09:42,290
Don't make your master worry.

154
00:09:42,290 --> 00:09:43,020
Don't worry.

155
00:09:44,270 --> 00:09:44,930
Master Bei,

156
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,440
I heard from my master

157
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,960
that you can write poetry.

158
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,360
At this moment of farewell,

159
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,420
how about one poem?

160
00:09:53,550 --> 00:09:54,080
Alright.

161
00:10:03,910 --> 00:10:06,200
The road ahead stretches endlessly,

162
00:10:06,790 --> 00:10:08,840
and the autumn wind is lonely.

163
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:11,530
If one stands in the wind too long,

164
00:10:12,510 --> 00:10:13,510
one will get cold.

165
00:10:17,870 --> 00:10:19,330
It is indeed getting cold.

166
00:10:20,750 --> 00:10:21,410
Master Bei,

167
00:10:22,560 --> 00:10:23,960
you should head back now.

168
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,250
Until we meet again.

169
00:10:25,670 --> 00:10:26,270
Take care.

170
00:10:32,030 --> 00:10:32,550
Mr. Bei,

171
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,740
if you later discover

172
00:10:35,030 --> 00:10:36,840
that he isn't your old friend's son,

173
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:40,170
but a lonely soul who came from
another world many years ago,

174
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:42,270
you'll definitely be heartbroken.

175
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,280
At that time,

176
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,180
will you still treat him the same way?

177
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:50,360
I have calculated the expected yield

178
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:52,440
during droughts based on
the crop varieties in each region.

179
00:10:52,440 --> 00:10:53,270
When a drought occurs,

180
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:55,390
Your Majesty, you can adjust
disaster relief according to

181
00:10:55,390 --> 00:10:56,840
the grain reserves of each province.

182
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,360
Thank you for your hard work, Mr. Cen.

183
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,840
It is my duty.

184
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,510
Your Majesty,

185
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,790
since the reduction of taxes and rents

186
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:04,200
and the implementation
of the Salt-for-Services Policy,

187
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,080
the people's livelihood
has greatly improved.

188
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,400
-I've visited the villages around...
-Although the Yan people

189
00:11:07,400 --> 00:11:08,720
live in a remote land,

190
00:11:09,480 --> 00:11:12,480
they have always coveted
the prosperity of Great Xia.

191
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:15,550
I remember in the original story,
once Xiahou Dan died,

192
00:11:15,550 --> 00:11:18,750
The King of Yan immediately took advantage
of the drought to launch an invasion,

193
00:11:18,750 --> 00:11:20,810
clashing fiercely with Prince Duan.

194
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:24,800
If this diplomatic mission fails,

195
00:11:25,320 --> 00:11:26,720
war will be unavoidable.

196
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:29,210
It seems we must prepare early

197
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,490
to avoid being defenseless

198
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:32,840
by the time.

199
00:11:32,840 --> 00:11:35,480
I have visited
over 10 villages near the capital.

200
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:37,750
And many fields of Yan millet
have been cultivated within the border.

201
00:11:37,750 --> 00:11:39,000
After a few planting seasons,

202
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,960
even without buying seeds from Yan State,

203
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:43,240
we should be able to handle droughts
in the future.

204
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,280
As General You said

205
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:46,740
-the day before yesterday...
-General You?

206
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:49,520
Your Majesty.

207
00:11:49,670 --> 00:11:51,480
Although General You
is the commander of the Right Army,

208
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,320
he has none of the bearing
of a true general.

209
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,670
With him stationed at the southern border,

210
00:11:54,670 --> 00:11:57,000
it will sooner or later become a disaster.

211
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,670
He has good judgment.

212
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:01,910
This man was a coward
in the original story.

213
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:05,140
During the Yan-Xia war,
he rushed to surrender.

214
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:06,910
He truly disgraces his title of general.

215
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:09,270
I don't expect him
to accomplish anything significant.

216
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,680
But with him in that post,

217
00:12:11,270 --> 00:12:12,400
I can't command him,

218
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:13,880
nor can Prince Duan.

219
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,870
That's actually not a bad thing.

220
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,120
-But the southern border...
-Mr. Li.

221
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:18,720
Stop worrying about others.

222
00:12:19,270 --> 00:12:21,240
Tell me about the Ministry of Revenue.

223
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,640
The Ministry of Revenue?

224
00:12:25,440 --> 00:12:26,700
Then there's even more

225
00:12:26,910 --> 00:12:27,790
to report.

226
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,910
What is this?

227
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,620
What nonsense is this?

228
00:12:43,200 --> 00:12:44,730
Take it back and rewrite it!

229
00:12:44,870 --> 00:12:46,070
Here, drink more.

230
00:12:46,510 --> 00:12:47,110
Lord Chen.

231
00:12:47,670 --> 00:12:48,270
Lord Chen.

232
00:12:49,150 --> 00:12:50,420
Can't you see I'm busy?

233
00:12:50,510 --> 00:12:51,550
Take it back and rewrite it.

234
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:52,150
Lord Chen.

235
00:12:52,960 --> 00:12:53,560
Lord Chen.

236
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,360
This is my corrected version.

237
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,690
Why are you everywhere?

238
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:57,670
Go away.

239
00:12:58,320 --> 00:12:59,380
In the past 5 years,

240
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,770
the population and common people
of more than 10 counties

241
00:13:00,770 --> 00:13:02,440
have neither increased nor decreased.

242
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:05,480
Thousands of acres of fertile farmland
have been seized by local gentry,

243
00:13:05,480 --> 00:13:08,480
and not a single person
in the Ministry of Revenue noticed.

244
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,200
After this,

245
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,830
I finally understand

246
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,440
why the records
in each province and county

247
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:14,900
are full of errors
without anyone noticing,

248
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,610
and why those officials
have been idle for years

249
00:13:16,610 --> 00:13:18,510
without anyone
holding them accountable.

250
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:19,030
It's simply because

251
00:13:19,030 --> 00:13:21,490
those land-grabbing gentry

252
00:13:21,790 --> 00:13:23,670
are backed by layers of local officials,

253
00:13:23,670 --> 00:13:25,600
and behind those damn officials

254
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,270
are all imperial relatives.

255
00:13:27,550 --> 00:13:28,100
Li!

256
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,630
If we investigate thoroughly,

257
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:30,480
in the entire Ministry of Revenue,

258
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:32,740
how many would dare claim they're clean?

259
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,480
If we investigate further,

260
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,630
it leads to the Empress Dowager.

261
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:37,680
Who can investigate? Who dares to?

262
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:48,900
If we let them hide their corruption,

263
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:50,030
when will this land

264
00:13:50,030 --> 00:13:51,760
ever see fairness and justice?

265
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:53,440
With a vicious woman in power

266
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,040
and no wise ruler to oversee,

267
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,320
no matter how much effort we put in,

268
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,840
it'll be all in vain.

269
00:14:09,240 --> 00:14:09,720
Li.

270
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,910
What you said is true.

271
00:14:12,270 --> 00:14:15,000
But determination alone
cannot change the situation.

272
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,000
If we want to investigate,

273
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:18,390
we can always use some connections
in the bureaucracy

274
00:14:18,390 --> 00:14:19,720
and find flexible ways.

275
00:14:20,030 --> 00:14:21,890
You want me to exploit loopholes?

276
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,750
Since none of us is willing to stand by,

277
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:25,080
making some compromises

278
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:26,120
is acceptable, isn't it?

279
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,440
How should we compromise?

280
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:29,480
Why don't you demonstrate it yourself,
Lord Er,

281
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,870
and show me?

282
00:14:33,120 --> 00:14:33,850
For example,

283
00:14:33,960 --> 00:14:37,150
we could arrange for some farmers
whose fertile land was seized

284
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,390
to file a petition to His Majesty,

285
00:14:38,390 --> 00:14:41,510
then have a palace servant
subtly report it to the Empress Dowager.

286
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,480
As for the Ministry of Revenue...

287
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,000
Minister,

288
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,650
I heard that after the treasury incident,

289
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:57,200
the Empress Dowager has been keeping
a close eye on the Ministry of Revenue.

290
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:58,360
In my humble opinion,

291
00:14:58,360 --> 00:14:59,480
a reform order

292
00:14:59,630 --> 00:15:01,360
will be issued sooner or later.

293
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:02,320
We might as well

294
00:15:02,320 --> 00:15:05,270
take the initiative and reform
before she orders it.

295
00:15:05,960 --> 00:15:08,340
At least everyone
can save face in the end.

296
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:11,410
You can rest assured
and leave this matter to me.

297
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,750
What do you think, My Lord?

298
00:15:12,750 --> 00:15:13,610
That's just...

299
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:15,480
That's the general idea.

300
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,750
Li, you're so eloquent.

301
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,510
Certainly you would put it in a nicer way.

302
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:19,690
That makes sense.

303
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:23,470
I believe that

304
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,670
whether a cat is black or white,

305
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:27,000
as long as it catches mice,
it's a good cat.

306
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,800
Even though our path now
is winding and tortuous,

307
00:15:30,510 --> 00:15:32,440
even the smallest efforts

308
00:15:32,510 --> 00:15:35,640
will eventually pile up
like grains of sand into a tower.

309
00:15:35,870 --> 00:15:37,670
Since Li has finished his report,

310
00:15:37,670 --> 00:15:39,150
let me proceed next.

311
00:15:39,200 --> 00:15:39,720
I haven't fini—

312
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:41,920
Mr. Er has important matters to report.

313
00:15:42,630 --> 00:15:43,550
Sit down.

314
00:15:43,750 --> 00:15:44,600
What are you doing?

315
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,530
That was enough.

316
00:15:45,590 --> 00:15:48,620
[Kunyu Palace]

317
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,900
Through all these hardships,

318
00:16:04,130 --> 00:16:05,730
thankfully I've had Yong'er

319
00:16:06,010 --> 00:16:07,410
by my side supporting me.

320
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:09,720
I...

321
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:11,880
will never let you down.

322
00:16:25,910 --> 00:16:27,510
Xie Yong'er, oh Xie Yong'er.

323
00:16:28,290 --> 00:16:29,200
What are you doing?

324
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:30,200
Do you want to die?

325
00:16:34,720 --> 00:16:36,960
Your Highness,
why has your period come early?

326
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,240
It's not time yet.

327
00:16:38,260 --> 00:16:38,600
I...

328
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:44,630
Well...

329
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:49,370
It's not the period.

330
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:51,320
Perhaps...

331
00:16:51,750 --> 00:16:52,440
I bumped...

332
00:16:52,910 --> 00:16:54,240
into something somewhere.

333
00:16:54,240 --> 00:16:55,400
Are you injured?

334
00:16:55,630 --> 00:16:57,670
If you're injured, why didn't you tell me?

335
00:16:57,670 --> 00:16:58,960
I'll go get Physician Xiao.

336
00:16:58,960 --> 00:16:59,490
I'm fine.

337
00:17:00,270 --> 00:17:01,370
How can you be fine?

338
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,720
If you're injured, you can't attend

339
00:17:02,720 --> 00:17:03,670
to His Majesty in the bedchamber.

340
00:17:03,670 --> 00:17:04,790
We need to report this
to the Service Room.

341
00:17:04,790 --> 00:17:06,170
I said I'm fine.

342
00:17:12,349 --> 00:17:13,950
I was so careless that night.

343
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,650
After all these nights of service,

344
00:17:15,650 --> 00:17:17,650
His Majesty hasn't even touched me.

345
00:17:18,250 --> 00:17:19,640
If I'm pregnant with Prince Duan's child,

346
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:21,920
the consequences would be unimaginable.

347
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:23,319
I need to think of an idea.

348
00:17:27,240 --> 00:17:29,840
Go prepare
two bright-colored outfits for me.

349
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:30,750
Tonight,

350
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:34,080
I'll go see His Majesty.

351
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:37,720
This way,

352
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:38,950
merchants will compete to transport grain

353
00:17:38,950 --> 00:17:40,030
in exchange for
Salt Transportation and Sales License.

354
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:41,510
The profits from salt trade are enormous.

355
00:17:41,510 --> 00:17:43,640
Merchants will naturally flock to it.

356
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:44,480
In the future,

357
00:17:44,640 --> 00:17:46,200
the fight to control the monopoly

358
00:17:46,200 --> 00:17:50,660
will lead to collusion between officials
and merchants, breeding corruption.

359
00:17:51,590 --> 00:17:53,400
But wasn't the Salt-for-Services Policy

360
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,680
your proposal?

361
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,590
Your Majesty,

362
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:01,880
every dynasty's policies have their flaws.

363
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:05,070
Today, the Salt-for-Services Policy
does benefit the people.

364
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:06,510
When its drawbacks become apparent,

365
00:18:06,510 --> 00:18:08,770
it should be replaced with new policies.

366
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:11,680
By then,

367
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:12,980
Er,

368
00:18:13,310 --> 00:18:15,840
you will already hold high office,
won't you?

369
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:17,310
No.

370
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,350
By that time,

371
00:18:21,110 --> 00:18:22,770
I should no longer be in court.

372
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,680
Those who hold high office

373
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:33,200
should be people like you.

374
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:34,750
The court by then

375
00:18:34,790 --> 00:18:36,750
will surely allow talents like you

376
00:18:36,770 --> 00:18:37,830
to achieve great things

377
00:18:37,830 --> 00:18:39,490
and realize their ambitions.

378
00:18:40,030 --> 00:18:40,640
Mr. Li,

379
00:18:41,270 --> 00:18:42,440
I have never forgotten

380
00:18:42,440 --> 00:18:44,350
what we said that day
on the pleasure boat.

381
00:18:44,350 --> 00:18:46,410
What we seek is not power or scheming,

382
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:49,140
but the wealth and well-being
of the people.

383
00:18:49,310 --> 00:18:51,240
Otherwise, how are we different

384
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,550
from Prince Duan's sycophants?

385
00:18:52,550 --> 00:18:54,270
How could we face Du

386
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,440
and fulfill our promises to him?

387
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:58,960
We must carry his sincerity

388
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:01,480
and spare no effort to support Great Xia.

389
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:03,010
We will do everything we can

390
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,270
to support our wise ruler.

391
00:19:05,270 --> 00:19:07,270
The corrupt officials will pay the price.

392
00:19:07,270 --> 00:19:07,930
We will soon

393
00:19:09,270 --> 00:19:10,730
restore your reputation.

394
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:14,310
Mr. Er is right.

395
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:17,640
Those who accomplish great things
do not get caught up in trivial matters.

396
00:19:17,640 --> 00:19:18,840
His Majesty once said

397
00:19:18,920 --> 00:19:19,930
we are one team,

398
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,030
each with strengths and weaknesses,

399
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:23,490
and should work together.

400
00:19:25,880 --> 00:19:26,590
Chen Danian

401
00:19:27,720 --> 00:19:29,380
only cares for wine and women.

402
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:31,640
Mr. Li, you don't like dealing with him.

403
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,680
I'll take on the burden.

404
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:34,720
Leave it to me.

405
00:19:37,880 --> 00:19:39,270
The Ministry of Works
has many tedious matters.

406
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:40,640
I am good with calculations.

407
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,070
Mr. Yang, if you need me,

408
00:19:42,590 --> 00:19:43,240
just ask.

409
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:48,560
I only know farming.

410
00:19:48,960 --> 00:19:49,690
My health...

411
00:19:50,860 --> 00:19:52,660
I might not be of much help to you.

412
00:19:53,790 --> 00:19:54,520
I'm ashamed.

413
00:19:56,160 --> 00:19:56,820
So ashamed.

414
00:20:06,310 --> 00:20:06,750
Cen,

415
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,240
you like farming.

416
00:20:08,550 --> 00:20:09,750
If your ox gets tired,

417
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:10,620
I'm strong.

418
00:20:11,030 --> 00:20:12,160
I can take its place.

419
00:20:22,110 --> 00:20:24,040
Prince Duan has an army of 100,000.

420
00:20:24,270 --> 00:20:26,400
The Empress Dowager has the entire court.

421
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:26,930
And we...

422
00:20:28,960 --> 00:20:30,160
only have each other.

423
00:20:35,840 --> 00:20:37,640
I'm not particularly talented,

424
00:20:38,330 --> 00:20:40,840
but being able
to meet all of you in this lifetime

425
00:20:40,840 --> 00:20:42,440
is reason enough for a toast.

426
00:20:48,070 --> 00:20:49,600
I'll use tea in place of wine

427
00:20:49,750 --> 00:20:50,880
and toast to you all.

428
00:20:50,970 --> 00:20:51,640
Your Highness.

429
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:52,500
Your Highness.

430
00:20:54,110 --> 00:20:55,770
The world is like a long night.

431
00:20:56,480 --> 00:20:58,810
Who could change it with a single cry?

432
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:01,770
But to struggle alongside you,

433
00:21:02,750 --> 00:21:04,080
even if we fall halfway,

434
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:12,000
I know I'm not alone.

435
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:22,960
Li Yunxi.

436
00:21:27,590 --> 00:21:28,390
Your Majesty.

437
00:21:28,480 --> 00:21:30,140
Keep organizing the records.

438
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,540
Don't tell anyone.

439
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,640
Give them directly to me.

440
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,600
They'll be useful someday.

441
00:21:41,070 --> 00:21:42,470
Thank you, Your Majesty.

442
00:21:42,550 --> 00:21:42,880
Rise.

443
00:21:52,550 --> 00:21:54,550
It's because people like them exist

444
00:21:55,110 --> 00:21:57,770
that it makes me feel
leaving everything behind

445
00:21:58,030 --> 00:21:59,230
would be despicable.

446
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,310
Then I...

447
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,900
should properly thank these ministers.

448
00:22:08,350 --> 00:22:10,080
They make me know I'm not alone.

449
00:22:12,960 --> 00:22:14,020
Stop imitating me.

450
00:22:15,510 --> 00:22:17,840
It's getting late. I should head back now.

451
00:22:19,870 --> 00:22:21,530
Why not stay for dinner first?

452
00:22:21,750 --> 00:22:22,240
Hot pot.

453
00:22:22,550 --> 00:22:23,350
Your Majesty!

454
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:24,720
Your Majesty!

455
00:22:25,240 --> 00:22:26,040
Your Majesty.

456
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:27,800
Your Majesty,

457
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,430
Consort Xie requests...

458
00:22:31,480 --> 00:22:32,210
an audience.

459
00:22:34,160 --> 00:22:35,490
I will take my leave now.

460
00:22:42,160 --> 00:22:43,000
Consort Xie?

461
00:22:44,070 --> 00:22:44,530
Well...

462
00:22:44,920 --> 00:22:46,000
the hot pot...

463
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,860
The secret passage is over there.

464
00:22:48,840 --> 00:22:51,570
Solidifying your image
of favoring Consort Xie?

465
00:22:52,270 --> 00:22:52,720
I think

466
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,880
you're just getting back at me

467
00:22:54,880 --> 00:22:57,740
for making Xie Yong'er serve you
in the bedchamber.

468
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:06,900
Just admit it.

469
00:23:07,610 --> 00:23:09,940
Seeing a bunch of women fighting over you,

470
00:23:10,680 --> 00:23:13,010
you're secretly enjoying it, aren't you?

471
00:23:14,930 --> 00:23:17,270
And now you're turning your head away?
What's that supposed to mean?

472
00:23:17,270 --> 00:23:19,160
I know men too well.

473
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:21,140
You say no with your mouth,

474
00:23:21,400 --> 00:23:23,600
but inside you're probably delighted.

475
00:23:26,830 --> 00:23:27,680
However,

476
00:23:28,350 --> 00:23:30,810
we just tricked Prince Duan
at Banyue House.

477
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:33,110
And Xie Yong'er came at this time...

478
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:36,050
Could she be snooping for Prince Duan?

479
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:38,530
I can't let her do that.

480
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,690
I'd better stay and keep watch.

481
00:23:41,200 --> 00:23:42,200
You're so stupid.

482
00:23:42,510 --> 00:23:44,570
What if Xie Yong'er manipulates you?

483
00:23:46,550 --> 00:23:47,720
It makes perfect sense.

484
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,120
Completely reasonable.

485
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:03,810
Greetings, Your Majesty.

486
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:05,920
My dear, you're here.

487
00:24:06,350 --> 00:24:07,880
I have prepared wine for...

488
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:14,440
I...

489
00:24:15,070 --> 00:24:15,880
have prepared the wine.

490
00:24:15,880 --> 00:24:17,830
Your Majesty,
please don't trouble yourself.

491
00:24:17,830 --> 00:24:19,490
I've already had some drinks.

492
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:23,550
Is she imitating me?

493
00:24:25,590 --> 00:24:27,120
Wine is the essence of food.

494
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:29,420
The more you drink, the younger you feel.

495
00:24:29,790 --> 00:24:31,320
Let's play a drinking game.

496
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:34,750
I don't want to play drinking games.

497
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:37,050
Then what do you want to do?

498
00:24:40,830 --> 00:24:43,500
I want you to guess

499
00:24:44,510 --> 00:24:45,690
what I have...

500
00:24:46,920 --> 00:24:48,160
in my sleeve.

501
00:25:01,000 --> 00:25:01,720
Flowers.

502
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,810
Xie Yong'er really knows how to flirt.

503
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,750
Can CEO Dan handle this?

504
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:09,820
Flowers...

505
00:25:15,190 --> 00:25:15,990
Your Majesty.

506
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:18,070
Your Majesty, would you like to see

507
00:25:18,070 --> 00:25:19,750
what I have...

508
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:22,420
underneath this robe?

509
00:25:23,750 --> 00:25:24,810
My dear, calm down.

510
00:25:27,720 --> 00:25:29,440
How did it fall down?

511
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:33,070
She's much more flirtatious than I am.

512
00:25:33,110 --> 00:25:34,640
You don't like this either?

513
00:25:35,550 --> 00:25:36,640
Then I guess

514
00:25:37,030 --> 00:25:38,750
you must want to know

515
00:25:39,350 --> 00:25:40,960
what's underneath...

516
00:25:42,790 --> 00:25:44,240
my skirt.

517
00:25:49,160 --> 00:25:51,290
Xie Yong'er, you're quite something!

518
00:25:51,760 --> 00:25:53,030
My dear, don't come any closer.

519
00:25:53,030 --> 00:25:54,030
You must be drunk.

520
00:25:54,200 --> 00:25:56,260
You can pretend I'm drunk if you want.

521
00:25:59,640 --> 00:26:00,400
Your Majesty!

522
00:26:00,400 --> 00:26:03,060
-Don't move!
-Your Majesty, what are you doing?

523
00:26:03,160 --> 00:26:03,590
Your Majesty!

524
00:26:03,590 --> 00:26:04,350
What's happening?

525
00:26:04,350 --> 00:26:07,010
-It hurts, Your Majesty!
-I can't see anything!

526
00:26:07,270 --> 00:26:08,400
Your Majesty, be gentle.

527
00:26:08,400 --> 00:26:09,140
It hurts!

528
00:26:10,790 --> 00:26:13,030
Your Majesty,
do you truly feel nothing for me?

529
00:26:13,030 --> 00:26:13,510
Yes.

530
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:14,880
An Xian!

531
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:19,490
I'm here.

532
00:26:20,550 --> 00:26:21,750
Consort Xie is drunk.

533
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:23,490
Send her back to her palace.

534
00:26:23,510 --> 00:26:23,800
Yes.

535
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:25,860
Guards!

536
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:32,550
Carry her away.

537
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:37,520
What's wrong with that silly girl
Xie Yong'er today?

538
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,960
-Doesn't she only care about Prince Duan?
-Your Majesty!

539
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:40,590
-Is it Prince Duan
-Your Majesty!

540
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:42,120
who made her put on this act?

541
00:26:42,350 --> 00:26:44,510
Or did Prince Duan
break Xie Yong'er's heart

542
00:26:44,510 --> 00:26:46,840
and she switched her target to Xiahou Dan?

543
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:48,380
What does she want?

544
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,440
You...

545
00:27:04,480 --> 00:27:05,030
I...

546
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,010
What are you doing here?

547
00:27:12,350 --> 00:27:13,310
I, uh...

548
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:15,790
I...

549
00:27:16,350 --> 00:27:17,010
I got stuck.

550
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:23,310
You got stuck?

551
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:27,580
I've been eating well lately.

552
00:27:28,440 --> 00:27:29,570
I've gained weight.

553
00:27:40,240 --> 00:27:41,030
Yu Wanyin,

554
00:27:41,030 --> 00:27:43,000
what have you become?

555
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:43,950
You...

556
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:46,030
You were eavesdropping!

557
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:48,350
You're like those jealous,

558
00:27:48,350 --> 00:27:50,750
brainless cannon fodder in novels!

559
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,270
How embarrassing!

560
00:27:56,920 --> 00:27:58,240
Why don't you come out first?

561
00:27:58,240 --> 00:27:58,900
She's gone.

562
00:28:00,070 --> 00:28:00,830
Forget it.

563
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,640
There are too many people around.

564
00:28:02,640 --> 00:28:04,200
It wouldn't look good
if someone sees me here.

565
00:28:04,200 --> 00:28:05,000
I'd better go.

566
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:06,440
I won't let anyone in.

567
00:28:09,310 --> 00:28:10,240
Forget it.

568
00:28:10,830 --> 00:28:13,070
Eunuch An just caught us.

569
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:14,800
I'm leaving.

570
00:28:31,920 --> 00:28:33,180
Xie Yong'er just left,

571
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:36,120
and Xiahou Dan came to check the tunnel.

572
00:28:36,480 --> 00:28:38,080
How did he know I hadn't left?

573
00:28:39,590 --> 00:28:40,920
I didn't make any sound.

574
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:43,920
Unless...

575
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:48,000
Unless he wanted to find me.

576
00:28:50,790 --> 00:28:51,720
He didn't expect

577
00:28:52,310 --> 00:28:54,170
that I witnessed the whole thing.

578
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:56,000
And he was embarrassed.

579
00:28:59,190 --> 00:29:01,300
♪ A letter, a line of words ♪

580
00:29:01,540 --> 00:29:02,850
♪ Picking up the pen again and again ♪

581
00:29:03,130 --> 00:29:05,330
♪ A cup of tea, a glass of wine ♪

582
00:29:05,650 --> 00:29:07,080
♪ Drinking alone, hard to get drunk ♪

583
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:09,510
♪ Words unspoken ♪

584
00:29:11,040 --> 00:29:13,500
♪ Shyness unhidden ♪

585
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:17,340
♪ Walking down a street together ♪

586
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:18,680
♪ Shoulder to shoulder ♪

587
00:29:19,180 --> 00:29:21,190
♪ Raising my head, lowering my eyes ♪

588
00:29:21,660 --> 00:29:23,020
♪ Blushing slightly ♪

589
00:29:23,120 --> 00:29:25,570
♪ A face flushed red at first sight ♪

590
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:26,390
Yu Wanyin.

591
00:29:27,120 --> 00:29:30,460
♪ A smile like a flower in my heart ♪

592
00:29:27,510 --> 00:29:29,910
Have you been living so comfortably lately

593
00:29:30,270 --> 00:29:32,000
that you actually have time
to think about such nonsense?

594
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:34,470
♪ Whose longing lingers day and night? ♪

595
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,240
What's more important,
love or staying alive?

596
00:29:35,140 --> 00:29:38,130
♪ Piling up stories
and countless thoughts ♪

597
00:29:35,510 --> 00:29:36,720
Staying alive, of course.

598
00:29:36,720 --> 00:29:38,570
That's the most important thing.

599
00:29:38,570 --> 00:29:40,470
♪ Walking through once, taking a glance ♪

600
00:29:40,700 --> 00:29:42,380
♪ All lingering and wandering ♪

601
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,300
♪ How many rains, how many winds? ♪

602
00:29:44,650 --> 00:29:46,310
♪ Looking back, it's all like smoke ♪

603
00:29:47,170 --> 00:29:50,280
♪ Watching the hazy world ♪

604
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:49,030
But tonight's moon

605
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:51,000
is so beautiful.

606
00:29:51,120 --> 00:29:53,530
♪ Who still guards that yearning? ♪

607
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:54,710
♪ Still unchanged ♪

608
00:29:55,210 --> 00:29:58,070
♪ Even if months and years
pass in a blink ♪

609
00:29:58,670 --> 00:30:00,120
♪ One thought for a lifetime ♪

610
00:30:00,230 --> 00:30:07,430
♪ Waiting for someone to appear ♪

611
00:30:20,590 --> 00:30:21,790
Move these out first.

612
00:30:25,110 --> 00:30:25,440
Here.

613
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:35,400
Your Highness.

614
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,130
Please rise.

615
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,550
The weather's getting cold.

616
00:30:37,550 --> 00:30:38,830
I made some ginger soup for everyone.

617
00:30:38,830 --> 00:30:39,680
Drink it while it's hot.

618
00:30:39,680 --> 00:30:40,550
Thank you, Your Highness.

619
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:42,010
Thank you, Your Highness.

620
00:30:42,510 --> 00:30:42,840
Here.

621
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:46,770
There's no rush with this secret passage.

622
00:30:47,550 --> 00:30:48,480
His Majesty said

623
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:50,400
this secret passage is used every day.

624
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,720
We must hurry to widen it.

625
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:53,350
We can't let Your Highness suffer.

626
00:30:53,350 --> 00:30:53,880
Every...

627
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,030
every day?

628
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:57,240
CEO Dan is embarrassing me.

629
00:30:58,680 --> 00:31:00,400
Why hasn't His Majesty
dismissed the court yet today?

630
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:01,260
Your Highness,

631
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:02,510
I heard they're still arguing over

632
00:31:02,510 --> 00:31:04,920
whether to let the Yan envoys
enter the city.

633
00:31:04,920 --> 00:31:06,200
His Majesty just left court

634
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:08,240
and got trapped in the Imperial Study.

635
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,040
Your Majesty,

636
00:31:09,110 --> 00:31:10,720
the Yan people
claim to be celebrating your birthday,

637
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:12,040
but everyone knows

638
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:14,200
what they really want to do.

639
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:15,550
Yes.

640
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:18,000
If we open the city gates
and welcome them in,

641
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:20,240
wouldn't that be like
inviting a wolf into the house,

642
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:22,170
leading to endless consequences?

643
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,310
Yes.

644
00:31:23,310 --> 00:31:24,110
That's right.

645
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:26,120
Minister, how do you know

646
00:31:27,110 --> 00:31:28,640
that the Yan people's visit

647
00:31:28,960 --> 00:31:30,090
is ill-intentioned

648
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:33,460
rather than genuinely seeking peace talks?

649
00:31:34,160 --> 00:31:34,920
Peace talks?

650
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,240
Your Majesty,

651
00:31:36,350 --> 00:31:37,600
we've been fighting for over ten years.

652
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:39,070
If they wanted to talk,
they would've done it earlier.

653
00:31:39,070 --> 00:31:40,750
Why would they wait until today?

654
00:31:40,750 --> 00:31:41,280
Exactly.

655
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,550
We have 100,000 troops
bravely fighting them at the border,

656
00:31:44,550 --> 00:31:47,440
yet the court wants to
welcome them as honored guests.

657
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:49,240
Your Majesty, if you insist on this,

658
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:51,880
it'll disappoint our soldiers
at the border.

659
00:31:52,310 --> 00:31:53,310
Yes, Your Majesty.

660
00:31:53,310 --> 00:31:55,510
This must be a conspiracy
by the Yan people.

661
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,920
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

662
00:31:56,920 --> 00:31:58,720
Please reconsider, Your Majesty.

663
00:31:58,720 --> 00:32:00,450
If we can truly hold peace talks

664
00:32:00,640 --> 00:32:02,240
and end the war at the border,

665
00:32:02,510 --> 00:32:03,840
these 100,000 soldiers

666
00:32:04,680 --> 00:32:06,480
can reunite with their families

667
00:32:06,830 --> 00:32:07,830
and enjoy peace.

668
00:32:09,550 --> 00:32:10,950
Won't that be a blessing?

669
00:32:11,070 --> 00:32:12,510
Your Majesty, you make it sound simple.

670
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:13,400
Over the past 10 years,

671
00:32:13,400 --> 00:32:15,480
we've paid such a heavy price.

672
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,790
Now that we have the upper hand,

673
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:18,070
we should press the advantage

674
00:32:18,070 --> 00:32:19,730
and wipe out the Yan people.

675
00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:21,880
Yet now you want to give up halfway.

676
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:22,760
How are we

677
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:25,210
supposed to explain this to the soldiers?

678
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:27,590
Yes, Mr. Cao is right.

679
00:32:27,640 --> 00:32:28,480
How can we explain to them?

680
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,090
Exactly.

681
00:32:29,350 --> 00:32:30,790
Please calm down.

682
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,590
What we're discussing now is

683
00:32:32,590 --> 00:32:35,160
whether to let them enter the city
to celebrate my birthday.

684
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,830
We're not talking about peace talks yet.

685
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:37,360
Besides,

686
00:32:37,680 --> 00:32:39,410
I observed the stars last night

687
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:41,940
and saw Saturn aligning with Jupiter.

688
00:32:42,160 --> 00:32:43,270
This foretells...

689
00:32:43,270 --> 00:32:46,070
You Imperial Astronomers
always go with the wind.

690
00:32:46,200 --> 00:32:47,240
If solving problems could really be done

691
00:32:47,240 --> 00:32:48,960
with just a few divinations like you do,

692
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,510
what would we ministers be for?

693
00:32:50,510 --> 00:32:51,960
Exactly!

694
00:32:52,590 --> 00:32:56,590
-Please reconsider, Your Majesty!
-Please reconsider, Your Majesty!

695
00:33:32,200 --> 00:33:34,750
We cannot invite the wolf into the house,
Your Majesty!

696
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:36,680
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!
-Yes, Your Majesty.

697
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:38,720
We can't let the Yan people
get into Great Xia!

698
00:33:38,720 --> 00:33:40,240
Your Majesty, please reconsider!

699
00:33:40,240 --> 00:33:41,880
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!
-Your Majesty.

700
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:44,240
We cannot invite the wolf into the house,
Your Majesty!

701
00:33:44,240 --> 00:33:45,040
Your Majesty!

702
00:33:45,590 --> 00:33:46,390
Your Majesty!

703
00:33:47,110 --> 00:33:48,590
-We can't do that!
-Your Majesty, please reconsider!

704
00:33:48,590 --> 00:33:50,030
Your Majesty, please reconsider!

705
00:33:50,030 --> 00:33:50,830
Your Majesty!

706
00:33:50,960 --> 00:33:52,830
We can't do that! We can!

707
00:33:52,830 --> 00:33:53,200
Your Majesty!

708
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,720
We can't do that!

709
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,350
Please reconsider, Your Majesty!

710
00:33:56,350 --> 00:33:57,150
Your Majesty!

711
00:33:57,830 --> 00:33:58,590
Your Majesty!

712
00:33:58,590 --> 00:33:59,270
Your Majesty!

713
00:33:59,270 --> 00:34:00,300
Your Majesty!

714
00:34:11,760 --> 00:34:12,760
This Xiahou Dan.

715
00:34:13,550 --> 00:34:14,760
It's almost dark.

716
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:16,460
Why hasn't he arrived yet?

717
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,659
I've been waiting for so long.

718
00:34:22,280 --> 00:34:24,280
He can't possibly be skipping dinner,
can he?

719
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,080
That won't do.

720
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,760
It's indeed much more spacious now.

721
00:34:43,250 --> 00:34:44,570
This Xiahou Dan.

722
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,920
If you're skipping dinner,

723
00:34:46,920 --> 00:34:49,520
you should at least send someone
to let me know.

724
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:51,199
Just how busy are you

725
00:34:51,960 --> 00:34:54,630
that you can't even spare the time
to send a message?

726
00:34:54,630 --> 00:34:56,630
This Xiahou Dan is driving me crazy!

727
00:35:02,710 --> 00:35:04,840
Yu Wanyin, what are you doing?

728
00:35:05,840 --> 00:35:07,480
You're now a demonic consort
who brings disaster to the country.

729
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,000
You used to be
a heartless corporate slave.

730
00:35:09,000 --> 00:35:09,860
Look at you now.

731
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:13,070
You're not focusing on your career,

732
00:35:13,070 --> 00:35:15,000
and you're even chasing after him.

733
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:15,960
Go back.

734
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:21,670
So what?

735
00:35:22,150 --> 00:35:23,590
If he truly has something urgent,

736
00:35:23,590 --> 00:35:24,450
isn't it normal

737
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:26,110
for me to go ask?

738
00:35:26,800 --> 00:35:27,440
Besides,

739
00:35:28,280 --> 00:35:29,440
isn't this secret passage

740
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:30,630
meant to be used?

741
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:36,050
He's coming.

742
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:38,130
Wanyin.

743
00:35:38,670 --> 00:35:39,840
I was just looking for you.

744
00:35:39,840 --> 00:35:40,500
Dan is sick.

745
00:35:40,670 --> 00:35:41,000
Come.

746
00:35:48,450 --> 00:35:50,240
Zhang San's Diary.

747
00:35:50,260 --> 00:35:51,710
When three people are together,

748
00:35:51,710 --> 00:35:54,570
there's always something
to learn from each other.

749
00:35:54,800 --> 00:35:55,970
I will select

750
00:35:55,970 --> 00:35:57,510
-their good qualities and follow them,
-The Empress Dowager is gone.

751
00:35:57,510 --> 00:35:59,630
-The Emperor doesn't care about me.
-their bad qualities

752
00:35:59,630 --> 00:36:01,800
-and avoid them.
-The new Empress is not a good person.

753
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,620
-Her eyes...
-Confucius said,

754
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:03,440
while standing by a river...

755
00:36:03,440 --> 00:36:05,840
Every time our eyes meet,
I get goosebumps.

756
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:08,390
Greetings, Your Majesty.

757
00:36:17,590 --> 00:36:18,070
Mother.

758
00:36:21,190 --> 00:36:22,530
You're studying?

759
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,630
Your Majesty,

760
00:36:25,230 --> 00:36:28,320
the Crown Prince has been studying
the Analects of Confucius lately.

761
00:36:28,320 --> 00:36:29,390
I thought

762
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:31,620
that as a Confucian classic,

763
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:35,000
it can teach him how to
cultivate himself and govern the state,

764
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,070
so that in the future

765
00:36:36,070 --> 00:36:38,930
he can shoulder the responsibilities
of the realm.

766
00:36:39,590 --> 00:36:40,920
The Analects of Confucius

767
00:36:40,920 --> 00:36:42,230
is profound.

768
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:45,380
The Crown Prince is still very young.

769
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,660
Might it be too difficult for him?

770
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,290
I believe

771
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:51,550
he should proceed step by step.

772
00:36:53,190 --> 00:36:55,630
What about the Thousand Character Classic?

773
00:36:55,630 --> 00:36:58,440
It is full of principles
on conduct and behavior,

774
00:36:59,630 --> 00:37:01,030
and would be easier

775
00:37:01,800 --> 00:37:03,460
for the Crown Prince to learn.

776
00:37:07,440 --> 00:37:09,590
Study the Thousand Character Classic?

777
00:37:09,590 --> 00:37:11,230
She's afraid I'll learn too much

778
00:37:11,230 --> 00:37:12,690
and become capable enough

779
00:37:12,760 --> 00:37:14,070
that she can no longer control me.

780
00:37:14,070 --> 00:37:15,110
Does she want to raise me
into a useless puppet

781
00:37:15,110 --> 00:37:16,640
she can manipulate at will?

782
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:17,680
No way.

783
00:37:18,190 --> 00:37:20,320
I can't just sit here waiting for doom.

784
00:37:22,190 --> 00:37:22,760
Dan,

785
00:37:24,030 --> 00:37:25,190
what do you think?

786
00:37:27,230 --> 00:37:27,760
Mother,

787
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:31,090
the Imperial Study is so quiet and lonely.

788
00:37:31,480 --> 00:37:33,480
I'm here alone every day,

789
00:37:33,960 --> 00:37:35,690
and it's truly lonely and dull.

790
00:37:36,760 --> 00:37:38,090
I beg for your kindness.

791
00:37:39,630 --> 00:37:40,950
Even one companion

792
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:41,960
would be nice.

793
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,100
Your Highness,

794
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:46,190
Her Majesty has instructed that

795
00:37:46,190 --> 00:37:46,850
from now on,

796
00:37:47,230 --> 00:37:48,440
the Second Prince

797
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:50,190
will study with you.

798
00:37:50,330 --> 00:37:53,020
[Young Xiahou Bo]

799
00:37:50,710 --> 00:37:52,400
Greetings, Your Highness.

800
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:54,200
Brother,

801
00:37:54,550 --> 00:37:55,950
no need for formalities.

802
00:37:58,280 --> 00:38:00,540
I was just worried about having no one...

803
00:38:01,800 --> 00:38:03,700
I will be a good study companion

804
00:38:03,880 --> 00:38:05,810
and not disappoint your kindness.

805
00:38:07,110 --> 00:38:09,070
He doesn't seem to like me much.

806
00:38:10,110 --> 00:38:11,110
It doesn't matter.

807
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:12,230
After spending time together,

808
00:38:12,230 --> 00:38:13,890
we'll surely become friends.

809
00:38:14,990 --> 00:38:18,270
[Thousand Character Classic]

810
00:38:15,110 --> 00:38:16,970
Dark is the sky, yellow the earth.

811
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:19,080
The universe was vast and crude.

812
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:21,760
The sun goes down, the moon comes up.

813
00:38:21,890 --> 00:38:23,550
The stars spread as dots.

814
00:38:24,480 --> 00:38:26,100
Winter succeeds summer.

815
00:38:26,670 --> 00:38:28,930
Autumn harvest follows winter storage.

816
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:31,180
The surplus days make a leap year.

817
00:38:31,510 --> 00:38:33,290
Music pipes regulate the sun.

818
00:38:51,320 --> 00:38:52,190
Your Highness,

819
00:38:52,880 --> 00:38:53,970
pay attention.

820
00:38:55,230 --> 00:38:55,750
Master,

821
00:38:56,070 --> 00:38:57,400
I was the one dozing off.

822
00:38:57,510 --> 00:38:58,800
You punished the wrong person.

823
00:38:58,800 --> 00:39:00,800
The Crown Prince has a noble status.

824
00:39:01,190 --> 00:39:02,280
Even if he makes mistakes,

825
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,440
the punishment should be taken by

826
00:39:03,440 --> 00:39:04,800
his study companion.

827
00:39:09,150 --> 00:39:09,610
Master,

828
00:39:10,400 --> 00:39:11,480
how can you do this?

829
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,420
I was the one who made the mistake.

830
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:15,350
I should be the one being punished.

831
00:39:15,550 --> 00:39:16,410
The other one.

832
00:39:30,360 --> 00:39:32,800
How is it that
after getting a study companion,

833
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,300
your studies

834
00:39:34,710 --> 00:39:36,250
have become even worse?

835
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:38,600
Why is that?

836
00:39:41,190 --> 00:39:41,650
Mother,

837
00:39:42,550 --> 00:39:43,430
I am foolish

838
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:45,520
and always anger the Master.

839
00:39:46,590 --> 00:39:48,110
I even caused trouble for my brother

840
00:39:48,110 --> 00:39:50,240
that he couldn't focus on his lessons.

841
00:39:50,360 --> 00:39:50,900
Perhaps

842
00:39:51,230 --> 00:39:52,280
the Master

843
00:39:53,280 --> 00:39:55,010
should tutor me alone instead.

844
00:39:55,590 --> 00:39:56,920
Crown Prince,

845
00:39:57,320 --> 00:39:59,980
you're the Crown Prince.
How could you be wrong?

846
00:40:00,800 --> 00:40:01,930
The study companion

847
00:40:01,990 --> 00:40:03,630
is here to assist you.

848
00:40:04,550 --> 00:40:05,830
If he's not attentive,

849
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:07,590
that's his fault.

850
00:40:10,960 --> 00:40:12,760
I failed
to properly support the Crown Prince

851
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,190
and disrupted his studies.

852
00:40:14,190 --> 00:40:15,990
Please punish me, Your Majesty.

853
00:40:17,760 --> 00:40:20,320
Who gave you permission
to speak in front of me?

854
00:40:20,320 --> 00:40:21,980
Your mother, that lowly maid,

855
00:40:22,190 --> 00:40:24,630
talked out of turn while serving

856
00:40:24,630 --> 00:40:25,800
the Crown Prince's birth mother

857
00:40:25,800 --> 00:40:27,710
and was slapped to death.

858
00:40:28,230 --> 00:40:30,690
Are you planning
to follow in her footsteps?

859
00:40:32,550 --> 00:40:33,210
I was wrong.

860
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,280
I will be careful with my words
and actions from now on

861
00:40:35,280 --> 00:40:37,880
and serve the Crown Prince
with full devotion.

862
00:40:42,550 --> 00:40:43,350
Crown Prince.

863
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:49,170
Don't be afraid, Crown Prince.

864
00:40:49,630 --> 00:40:51,030
There's no need to worry.

865
00:40:52,110 --> 00:40:54,800
Your father has many sons.

866
00:40:55,510 --> 00:40:57,040
If he doesn't perform well,

867
00:40:57,440 --> 00:41:00,040
I can simply find you
another study companion.

868
00:41:07,910 --> 00:41:11,070
[Thousand Character Classic]

869
00:41:30,630 --> 00:41:32,360
All of you, hold out your hands.

870
00:41:39,330 --> 00:41:39,790
Master,

871
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:41,530
I wasn't dozing off.

872
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:43,530
Why are you punishing them?

873
00:41:44,030 --> 00:41:46,000
Her Majesty specifically instructed

874
00:41:46,000 --> 00:41:47,800
that when the Crown Prince's headaches
act up,

875
00:41:47,800 --> 00:41:50,030
someone beside him
must feel even more pain

876
00:41:50,030 --> 00:41:50,880
to relieve it.

877
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,560
Master! Master!

878
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:53,510
I'm not in pain!

879
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:54,590
I forbid you to hit them!

880
00:41:54,590 --> 00:41:55,370
Crown Prince, why are you

881
00:41:55,370 --> 00:41:56,320
-pretending to be kind?
-Master!

882
00:41:56,320 --> 00:41:57,630
With Her Majesty caring about you,

883
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:59,480
you should take better care
of your precious self.

884
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,210
Master!

885
00:42:02,360 --> 00:42:03,710
We dare not let you plead for us.

886
00:42:03,710 --> 00:42:08,040
I'll take a few hits and consider it
dispelling misfortune for Your Highness.

887
00:42:08,320 --> 00:42:09,400
Master! Master!

888
00:42:09,480 --> 00:42:10,080
No crying!

889
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,190
Hold out your hand!

890
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:11,710
Master!

891
00:42:13,070 --> 00:42:14,730
Sixth Brother is still young.

892
00:42:15,000 --> 00:42:15,850
I'll take the punishment in his place!
